Fire Pit BBQ Grill Smoker Table Outdoor Garden Ice Pits Wood Firepit Sometimes the cold does bring out the best of everything. Especially if you have the 4-in-1 Fire Pit BBQ.Naturally, with winter, the Fire Pit, whether it's wood or charcoal fired, is absolutely wonderful with its warm-creating capabilities. Nothing like chilling around the Pit for a bit of social pow wow in the wintry outdoors. Better still, lay on a great BBQ while reminiscing cherished memories simply by placing the BBQ grill over the pit. Great food and endearing conversation are simply inseparable in moments like these. And there's still plenty of space around the Fire Pit to place your drinks, snacks and desserts to keep the good times going well after the main course.Without the flames, the Fire Pit doubles up as a snazzy alfresco outdoor table. Just cover the centre with the supplied mesh dome for a simple rustic transformation. What's more, it can even serve as a gigantic ice pit where the included huge ice tray can take its place in the centre hollow. Top it with ice and drinks for refreshing escapades all summer long.Designed to be strong, rust-resistant and able to withstand any inclement weather or high heat condition, the robust 4-in-1 Fire Pit BBQ is a must-have for anyone who enjoys entertaining outdoors winter, spring, summer or fall.Come on baby, light my fire!

Studies have proven that this sleep is essential for processing difficult emotions (such as grief), managing complicated situations, and developing creative solutions (the ones you remember in your morning shower) In other words, this sleep is essential for mental and emotional health. Mini Flag Nordic matta har ritat möbler och andra produkter för ASPLUND sedan 1990. Allt ifrån pallar och stolar till speglar och mattor. Både för ASPLUNDs internationella möbelkollektioner och specialprodukter för deras butiks sortiment. Thomas Sandell är född 1959, arkitekt SIR och SAR. Ordförande i SAR, Svenska Arkitekters Riksförbund, han har genom åren mottagit en rad olika design- och arkitekturutmärkelser. Idag är Sandell en av Sveriges mest framgångsrika designer/arkitekter, med prestigefyllda uppdrag såväl i Sverige som i utlandet.

Möbelföretaget är ett av de mest tekniskt avancerade och betydelsefulla i Europa.

Natural Geo Spontaneous Jute Handwoven Charcoal/Multi Abstract Area Rug Regular care is essential to the longevity of your rug. Due to the nature of jute fibers, light shedding is normal and will diminish over time with vacuuming. Because of the organic composition of the rug, it's normal to expect extra jute particles to shed off the rug for the first 3-4 weeks after initially laying the new area rug into place. Regular vacuuming is recommended without the use of beater bars to avoid threads being pulled. Spills should be absorbed thoroughly, then spot cleaned with mild soap and water. It’s normal for loose ends to show up from time to time with absolutely any area rug, however it’s important to snip them with a scissor immediately - pulling on loose ends by hand is harmful to the strength of your rug. As these rugs are handcrafted, please note that each craftsman's workmanship can vary, thus although your rug will be very similar in pattern as shown in the photos, slight and negligible variation is to be expected. Rug tolerances on either length and width can vary by +/- 3 inches in relation to the advertised size. A non-skid pad is recommended to provide additional cushioning, and to prevent slippage.
